<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="65800000t" end="99300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">C班的话剧即将开演</p>
<p begin="109500000t" end="155600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">请各位观众坐在座位上 不要走动</p>
<p begin="177400000t" end="196700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">伊莉娜同学太棒了</p>
<p begin="196700000t" end="210200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">好帅气</p>
<p begin="229700000t" end="248100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">来了好多观众啊</p>
<p begin="275500000t" end="291600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">莉迪姐姐</p>
<p begin="296300000t" end="311400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">终于要开始了呢</p>
<p begin="311400000t" end="347200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">虽然我演的是一个小配角 不过还是好激动啊</p>
<p begin="347200000t" end="363500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">别 别别别这样说啊</p>
<p begin="363500000t" end="391600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">害得我更更更紧张了</p>
<p begin="394300000t" end="421500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">伊莉娜小姐 请冷静</p>
<p begin="421500000t" end="455600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">别想着要完美演绎 回应观众的期待之类的</p>
<p begin="458900000t" end="485600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">把这些念头都抛在脑后吧</p>
<p begin="489000000t" end="531700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">二位只要出场就能让舞台熠熠生辉了</p>
<p begin="536200000t" end="547400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">放轻松</p>
<p begin="551800000t" end="572500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">就 就就就就是说嘛</p>
<p begin="572500000t" end="606000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">亚 亚亚亚亚德这样一说说说</p>
<p begin="606000000t" end="635400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">我 我我我就轻松多了</p>
<p begin="635400000t" end="663600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">谢 谢谢谢谢你…</p>
<p begin="663600000t" end="677200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">好像没效果啊</p>
<p begin="837500000t" end="870300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">足以融化孤独的呼声</p>
<p begin="870300000t" end="908600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">究竟来自说？</p>
<p begin="914700000t" end="958900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">向往温暖的我 该走了。</p>
<p begin="958900000t" end="976300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">再来一次，一次，一次！</p>
<p begin="981100000t" end="998100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">咏唱 交个朋友</p>
<p begin="998100000t" end="1014500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">解除 扑克脸</p>
<p begin="1014500000t" end="1045900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">完全等身大的 坦诚交谈</p>
<p begin="1047500000t" end="1065100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">打破墙壁 转移魔法</p>
<p begin="1065100000t" end="1081100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">瞬间便融洽相处</p>
<p begin="1081100000t" end="1097200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">共鸣之和谐 打破孤独！</p>
<p begin="1097200000t" end="1110900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">精准无比 是不是很完美？！</p>
<p begin="1110900000t" end="1174400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">沉默寡言的挑战者 迈出第一步</p>
<p begin="1174400000t" end="1228300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">生涩的自己也要抱紧</p>
<p begin="1232200000t" end="1266300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">一起开始尝试！就是现在 尝试！</p>
<p begin="1269600000t" end="1307700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">向奇迹发起挑战吧</p>
<p begin="1307700000t" end="1348000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">无敌的心情 永远心连着心</p>
<p begin="1348000000t" end="1365000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">魅力四射 魅力四射</p>
<p begin="1365000000t" end="1398800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">鼓足干劲 尝试！发展超乎想像</p>
<p begin="1401300000t" end="1433100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">点燃勇气</p>
<p begin="1433100000t" end="1472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">即使现在相隔遥远</p>
<p begin="1472600000t" end="1507000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">有朝一日 也必定能相互理解</p>
<p begin="1507000000t" end="1522700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">做我的朋友！！！</p>
<p begin="1522700000t" end="1576400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">哔哩哔哩译制<br />Translated by bilibili</p>
<p begin="1606900000t" end="1632800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">要是能听见我说话 就给我站起来战斗</p>
<p begin="1638000000t" end="1656400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">我绝不允许你们放弃</p>
<p begin="1702300000t" end="1740100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">怀着恐惧颤抖吧 你们这帮低等生物</p>
<p begin="1833300000t" end="1857300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">我要奋勇杀出一条血路</p>
<p begin="1860700000t" end="1877500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">跟着你们的「魔王」冲啊</p>
<p begin="1883500000t" end="1908400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">这比想像中更羞耻啊</p>
<p begin="1908400000t" end="1931000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">居然要演美化过的自己</p>
<p begin="1934300000t" end="1945300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">太棒了</p>
<p begin="1952500000t" end="1969800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">亚德大人太帅了</p>
<p begin="1969800000t" end="1987900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">跟真魔王似的</p>
<p begin="1996200000t" end="2014300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">不过 真是触景生情啊</p>
<p begin="2019400000t" end="2055800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我想起了这场与「阿维亚·德萨·威尔斯」的战斗</p>
<p begin="2063900000t" end="2089100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">真是场极其异样的战斗</p>
<p begin="2105700000t" end="2121800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">战术跟往常一样</p>
<p begin="2124700000t" end="2160100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我和莉迪娅先冲锋陷阵 弄清敌方的情报</p>
<p begin="2163900000t" end="2189100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">对此有异议的人请举手</p>
<p begin="2203600000t" end="2234200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">我才不放心让你保护姐姐</p>
<p begin="2237000000t" end="2249000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">所以由我去…</p>
<p begin="2249000000t" end="2270700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">少啰唆 你给我闭嘴</p>
<p begin="2279600000t" end="2293100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">可 可是…</p>
<p begin="2296800000t" end="2330500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">喊你闭嘴 没听见吗</p>
<p begin="2347800000t" end="2379300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我还不是…我还不是…</p>
<p begin="2394500000t" end="2407800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">蝼蚁们</p>
<p begin="2415100000t" end="2436900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我会等到明天中午再进攻</p>
<p begin="2439700000t" end="2455700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">你们就好好商量吧</p>
<p begin="2461400000t" end="2493400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">另外 今晚尽情吃喜欢的东西吧</p>
<p begin="2493400000t" end="2520700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">有恋人就缠绵个够</p>
<p begin="2525500000t" end="2556200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">因为等到明天就再也没机会了</p>
<p begin="2689100000t" end="2710400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">那个 巴尔 可以聊聊吗</p>
<p begin="2713400000t" end="2722400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">怎么了</p>
<p begin="2727400000t" end="2759800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">你觉得我是废物吗</p>
<p begin="2785500000t" end="2811600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我还不是能帮上忙</p>
<p begin="2817300000t" end="2838500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">又不会拖大家的后退</p>
<p begin="2838500000t" end="2863000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">为了保护大家 我都变强了</p>
<p begin="2866900000t" end="2905600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">我们看在眼里的 我和莉迪娅都认可你的实力</p>
<p begin="2905600000t" end="2928800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">那是为什么 刚才就是…</p>
<p begin="2932800000t" end="2958100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">那是因为我们不想失去你</p>
<p begin="2962700000t" end="3000000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">尤其是莉迪娅 她想让你接班</p>
<p begin="3015300000t" end="3039600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">虽然你跟莉迪娅很像 又没耐心又傻</p>
<p begin="3042800000t" end="3076500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">但你能为了他人拼尽全力 没几个人能做到</p>
<p begin="3080100000t" end="3122000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">可…可是 我想帮助莉迪娅姐姐</p>
<p begin="3140400000t" end="3167400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">好吧 你就放手去干吧</p>
<p begin="3170800000t" end="3185900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">我替你承担责任</p>
<p begin="3193900000t" end="3219500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">巴尔 谢谢你</p>
<p begin="3219500000t" end="3235200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">我会努力的</p>
<p begin="3252500000t" end="3288500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">只不过 你要把自身安全放在第一位哦</p>
<p begin="3297200000t" end="3339200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">因为你要是死了 我也会有点伤心的</p>
<p begin="3405100000t" end="3447300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你过去似乎杀了我很多同胞</p>
<p begin="3451700000t" end="3489800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">不过这一切今天就到头了</p>
<p begin="3495500000t" end="3514300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">圣剑「德米斯·阿尔吉斯」</p>
<p begin="3517500000t" end="3572500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">我就用手中最强的宝物送你们上路吧</p>
<p begin="3623300000t" end="3640400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">我来了 蝼蚁们</p>
<p begin="3643600000t" end="3670700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">让你们见识下真正的绝望…</p>
<p begin="3847200000t" end="3860800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">啊？别 等…</p>
<p begin="3929100000t" end="3953500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">成功了 我成功了</p>
<p begin="3965900000t" end="4000700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我设下的陷阱重创了敌人</p>
<p begin="4029700000t" end="4059300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">瞧瞧你干的好事 希尔菲·梅尔海文</p>
<p begin="4059300000t" end="4095100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">我浑身上下的火热激情该如何宣泄</p>
<p begin="4123200000t" end="4139500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">老大</p>
<p begin="4139500000t" end="4156900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">你妈的 竟敢伤害老大</p>
<p begin="4198900000t" end="4217800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">我问你 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="4221600000t" end="4243400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">这陷阱是你设下的对吧</p>
<p begin="4247100000t" end="4266000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">没错</p>
<p begin="4266000000t" end="4298500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">这样一来 这次的最大功臣肯定就是我了</p>
<p begin="4303000000t" end="4320700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">嗯 是啊</p>
<p begin="4328500000t" end="4368800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">那么 你肯定记得陷阱的位置吧</p>
<p begin="4372600000t" end="4405700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">啊？我在战场每个角落都设下了陷阱</p>
<p begin="4409500000t" end="4429300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">怎么可能全部记下来嘛</p>
<p begin="4452900000t" end="4484700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">这样啊这样啊 那我问你 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="4484700000t" end="4514200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">我们该怎样离开这里呢</p>
<p begin="4532100000t" end="4550400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">那就是 那个…</p>
<p begin="4565400000t" end="4574700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">靠气势？</p>
<p begin="4577600000t" end="4605300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">你这蠢货</p>
<p begin="4680500000t" end="4704200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">太…太过分了</p>
<p begin="4706500000t" end="4733600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">怎么能这样对待最大功臣</p>
<p begin="4739400000t" end="4770700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">当初不是你说要替我负责吗</p>
<p begin="4770700000t" end="4791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">大骗子</p>
<p begin="4791800000t" end="4814000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">看来根本没反省啊</p>
<p begin="4816900000t" end="4850400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">看来还得来三遍奥利维安的全套地狱级教育</p>
<p begin="4850400000t" end="4874100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">差不多可以原谅她了吧</p>
<p begin="4880700000t" end="4893500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">虽然发生了不少事</p>
<p begin="4897000000t" end="4932200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">但是多亏了希尔菲 我们一个人都没死</p>
<p begin="4942000000t" end="4982200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">想想我们过去的经历 这已经超越奇迹了吧</p>
<p begin="4986000000t" end="5037900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">我的妹妹真的每次都能干出好玩的事</p>
<p begin="5055900000t" end="5103500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">还是莉迪姐姐更懂信赏必罚</p>
<p begin="5103500000t" end="5117700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">希尔菲</p>
<p begin="5124500000t" end="5149000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">算啦算啦 这事就到此为止吧</p>
<p begin="5165700000t" end="5195800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">希尔菲 你已经足够厉害了</p>
<p begin="5200990000t" end="5226300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">不过呢 你有点太拼了</p>
<p begin="5234690000t" end="5254500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">你用不着承担这么多的</p>
<p begin="5258200000t" end="5276800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">你要相信同伴 勇往直前</p>
<p begin="5285300000t" end="5305600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">开会时吼了你 真抱歉</p>
<p begin="5309100000t" end="5339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">当时我是想不到更合适的说法</p>
<p begin="5437500000t" end="5454000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">演出大获成功啊</p>
<p begin="5454000000t" end="5461900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">- 嗯<br />- 是的</p>
<p begin="5466400000t" end="5489600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">好在希尔菲小姐忘词时</p>
<p begin="5489600000t" end="5528000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">亚德同学靠即兴表演救了场</p>
<p begin="5528000000t" end="5567900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">真是的 演到一半就不按剧本演了</p>
<p begin="5567900000t" end="5585900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">搞得我提心吊胆的</p>
<p begin="5613800000t" end="5633500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">太好了 演出成功了</p>
<p begin="5636500000t" end="5666600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">我添了那么多麻烦 大家却对我这么好</p>
<p begin="5717900000t" end="5745200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">明天校庆就要结束了呢</p>
<p begin="5750800000t" end="5773100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">只剩下武斗会的决赛</p>
<p begin="5773100000t" end="5796900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">还有后夜晚会的精神节了啊</p>
<p begin="5807200000t" end="5834500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">到头来没出任何问题啊</p>
<p begin="5837300000t" end="5863200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">那封恐吓信究竟是怎么回事呢</p>
<p begin="5880600000t" end="5916900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">怪了 希尔菲小姐上哪儿去了</p>
<p begin="5961300000t" end="5972800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">姐姐</p>
<p begin="6073800000t" end="6100400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">我好想你啊 姐姐</p>
<p begin="6255700000t" end="6274600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">希尔菲小姐怎么还不来</p>
<p begin="6274600000t" end="6292500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">会不会遇上什么事了</p>
<p begin="6292500000t" end="6337900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">嗯 伊莉娜小姐说她演出结束后就不太对劲</p>
<p begin="6346900000t" end="6360600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">这说不定是…</p>
<p begin="6373600000t" end="6386900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">沦陷了</p>
<p begin="6395000000t" end="6413400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">什…什么意思啊</p>
<p begin="6417600000t" end="6445200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">昨天演出时亚德帮了她</p>
<p begin="6445200000t" end="6470100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">于是就动心了 肯定是这样</p>
<p begin="6474300000t" end="6498800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">不不不 这怎么可能</p>
<p begin="6498800000t" end="6516300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">不会错的</p>
<p begin="6516300000t" end="6554700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">我觉得近期肯定会发生告白事件</p>
<p begin="6554700000t" end="6582800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">别啊 放…放过我吧</p>
<p begin="6591000000t" end="6606200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">一说就来了</p>
<p begin="6649400000t" end="6660600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">那个 亚德</p>
<p begin="6664000000t" end="6688900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">这场比赛我一定会赢的</p>
<p begin="6701900000t" end="6737900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">等大赛结束后 希望你能来下「剑王树」</p>
<p begin="6780500000t" end="6793000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">祝你好运</p>
<p begin="6793000000t" end="6803200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">不不不</p>
<p begin="6818900000t" end="6846600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">今年的大赛充满了意外</p>
<p begin="6846600000t" end="6869600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">冠军的有力争夺者接连出局</p>
<p begin="6869600000t" end="6888300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">黑马一路杀出重围</p>
<p begin="6888300000t" end="6915300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">决赛也是万万没有料到的</p>
<p begin="6921200000t" end="6937900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">我可不会输 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="6966100000t" end="7006900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">敬请欣赏备受瞩目的一战 比赛开始</p>
<p begin="7098500000t" end="7130700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">胜负已分 胜者 希尔菲选手</p>
<p begin="7358300000t" end="7383700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">喂 金妮 这是要干什么啊</p>
<p begin="7383700000t" end="7400100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">安静 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="7411100000t" end="7429900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">这肯定是准备告白吧</p>
<p begin="7429900000t" end="7437900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">什么</p>
<p begin="7437900000t" end="7453300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我去制止她</p>
<p begin="7453300000t" end="7466700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">等…等一下</p>
<p begin="7466700000t" end="7495000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">快 放 开 我 啊</p>
<p begin="7495000000t" end="7519600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">别去打扰啊</p>
<p begin="7530200000t" end="7540900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">希尔菲小姐</p>
<p begin="7552200000t" end="7565700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">让你久等了</p>
<p begin="7600600000t" end="7617400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">那个 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="7623100000t" end="7666400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">来到这里后 我就一直注视着你</p>
<p begin="7674900000t" end="7702300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">为了看清你到底是不是巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="7713900000t" end="7726000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">听我说 亚德</p>
<p begin="7726000000t" end="7749800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">我吧 对你…</p>
<p begin="7756100000t" end="7768300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">希尔菲小姐？</p>
<p begin="7774500000t" end="7797400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">我对你…</p>
<p begin="7810700000t" end="7830400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">恨之入骨 只想杀了你</p>
<p begin="7954400000t" end="7992400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">「我」「在此」「宣布」「解除封印」</p>
<p begin="8071500000t" end="8092600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">不是普通的复制品吗</p>
<p begin="8097000000t" end="8118500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">圣剑「巴尔特·加里古拉斯」</p>
<p begin="8121300000t" end="8155600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">曾经的勇者莉迪娅钟爱的神造武器</p>
<p begin="8160400000t" end="8195600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">被「剑王树」封印的东西就是这个</p>
<p begin="8200500000t" end="8243500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">竟然就藏在您所在的学园 实在是有趣</p>
<p begin="8243500000t" end="8267300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">这就叫命运弄人吗</p>
<p begin="8270000000t" end="8308100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">不管怎样 这下我就达成一个目的了</p>
<p begin="8308100000t" end="8323200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">希尔菲 你…</p>
<p begin="8328900000t" end="8342600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">「德米斯·阿尔吉斯」</p>
<p begin="8456200000t" end="8466500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">「阿尔斯特拉」</p>
<p begin="8470600000t" end="8482100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">「弗特普利斯」</p>
<p begin="8488100000t" end="8501900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">「特内布里克」</p>
<p begin="8556300000t" end="8588900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我要宰了你 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="8602300000t" end="8626400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">去死 去死去死</p>
<p begin="8636900000t" end="8646200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">「天空漫步者」</p>
<p begin="8704500000t" end="8722400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">希尔菲的样子不对劲</p>
<p begin="8725500000t" end="8744400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">是被人洗脑了吗</p>
<p begin="8774500000t" end="8788000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">出什么事了</p>
<p begin="8788000000t" end="8799700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">不知道</p>
<p begin="8805500000t" end="8844700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">啊 多么精彩的喜剧啊</p>
<p begin="8844700000t" end="8894500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">少女手持过往老师的武器 欲为其报仇</p>
<p begin="8894500000t" end="8929900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">比起无聊的戏剧 这要好看多了</p>
<p begin="8947500000t" end="8991600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">虽然你说过亚德·奥特梅尔是魔王的转生体</p>
<p begin="8995200000t" end="9017500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">但我不这样想</p>
<p begin="9017500000t" end="9059700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">真受不了 您还是如此愚蠢啊</p>
<p begin="9063200000t" end="9094800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">他是魔王转生体是千真万确的事实</p>
<p begin="9094800000t" end="9109100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">就算我这样说</p>
<p begin="9109100000t" end="9151100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">蠢到对仇敌怀有好感笨蛋也听不进去</p>
<p begin="9151100000t" end="9189900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">所以 我还是强行控制您好了</p>
<p begin="9317700000t" end="9340800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">永别了 我的朋友</p>
<p begin="9438200000t" end="9471900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我给您看的是几千年前的真相</p>
<p begin="9476300000t" end="9511800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">「勇者莉迪娅」从世上消失了</p>
<p begin="9511800000t" end="9542300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">去杀死仇敌 消灭魔王</p>
<p begin="9545000000t" end="9580300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">您就只剩这一个存在意义了</p>
<p begin="9603300000t" end="9629600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">注定的结局不会改变</p>
<p begin="9632800000t" end="9659200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">在最后小丑完美演绎了小丑</p>
<p begin="9659200000t" end="9684800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">故事以喜剧落幕</p>
<p begin="9684800000t" end="9716700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">实在是实在是太愉快了</p>
<p begin="9735900000t" end="9753200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">去死</p>
<p begin="9825600000t" end="9857200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">死了 死了死了</p>
<p begin="9860100000t" end="9878100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">我成功了 姐姐</p>
<p begin="9895200000t" end="9907400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">姐姐</p>
<p begin="10012900000t" end="10034100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">姐姐不在了</p>
<p begin="10040100000t" end="10064400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">姐姐不在的破世界</p>
<p begin="10068000000t" end="10086700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">「薇尔」「斯缇娜」…</p>
<p begin="10089500000t" end="10102200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">你在干什么</p>
<p begin="10111100000t" end="10134300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">你知道自己在干什么吗</p>
<p begin="10153700000t" end="10165600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">高级护盾</p>
<p begin="10231200000t" end="10264400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">我不会手下留情了 希尔菲小姐</p>
<p begin="10303690000t" end="10314090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">怎么会…</p>
<p begin="10314090000t" end="10336900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">伊莉娜小姐 我来助阵…</p>
<p begin="10379600000t" end="10389800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">金妮</p>
<p begin="10394190000t" end="10419500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">希尔菲 我会阻止你的</p>
<p begin="10426690000t" end="10448200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">我要把你也杀了</p>
<p begin="10450600000t" end="10463600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">因为我是…</p>
<p begin="10471190000t" end="10480000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">我是…</p>
<p begin="10488000000t" end="10509600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">你的大姐啊</p>
<p begin="10509600000t" end="10523300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">快住手 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="10574700000t" end="10591600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">二位没事吧</p>
<p begin="10604700000t" end="10612200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">亚德</p>
<p begin="10612200000t" end="10648000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">魔王 魔王 魔王！</p>
<p begin="10648000000t" end="10663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">快住手吧 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="10690900000t" end="10703200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">去死吧</p>
<p begin="10710800000t" end="10734600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">驱散魔法也无法解除洗脑吗</p>
<p begin="10741700000t" end="10772200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">那么 就只剩一个办法了</p>
<p begin="10799700000t" end="10834100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">我不想让你这激动勇者沦为杀戮者</p>
<p begin="10839200000t" end="10886500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">我希望你在人们心中是名垂千古的战士</p>
<p begin="10908400000t" end="10946600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">所以我才会 将你…</p>
<p begin="10984200000t" end="10991000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">5</p>
<p begin="11006400000t" end="11013900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">4</p>
<p begin="11031900000t" end="11039100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">3</p>
<p begin="11054800000t" end="11062300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">2</p>
<p begin="11080200000t" end="11088900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">1</p>
<p begin="11150000000t" end="11162600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">快住手 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="11212400000t" end="11224600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">姐姐？</p>
<p begin="11309700000t" end="11320100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="11326800000t" end="11341400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">真是的</p>
<p begin="11346000000t" end="11388000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">没用到这个地步 还真是让人生不起气啊</p>
<p begin="11448200000t" end="11464800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">你这输家</p>
<p begin="11468600000t" end="11498500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">给希尔菲洗脑的就是你吗</p>
<p begin="11502600000t" end="11513200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">是又怎样？</p>
<p begin="11518300000t" end="11533000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">你的目的是什么</p>
<p begin="11537800000t" end="11548900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">是您啊</p>
<p begin="11551600000t" end="11577700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">我们盼望着复活主人</p>
<p begin="11587800000t" end="11630400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">为此 就需要献祭那位大小姐</p>
<p begin="11630400000t" end="11665700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">所以您的存在就无比碍事</p>
<p begin="11669000000t" end="11701000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">于是 为了除掉你 我们就发起了行动</p>
<p begin="11703900000t" end="11727000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">好了 那我就上了</p>
<p begin="11845900000t" end="11864200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">「阿尔斯特拉」「弗特普」…</p>
<p begin="11864200000t" end="11873000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">太慢了</p>
<p begin="11914500000t" end="11938500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">你配不上那把剑</p>
<p begin="11997700000t" end="12023300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">我要让您和王都一起化为灰烬</p>
<p begin="12031800000t" end="12058300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">「薇尔」「斯缇娜」「奥尔维」…</p>
<p begin="12129500000t" end="12169500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">圣剑会选择主人 看来你没被选上啊</p>
<p begin="12214400000t" end="12253400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">看好了 圣剑是这样用的</p>
<p begin="12258900000t" end="12294400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">「薇尔」「斯缇娜」「奥尔维迪斯」</p>
<p begin="12294400000t" end="12308200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">什…什么</p>
<p begin="12369300000t" end="12396800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">这怎么可能</p>
<p begin="12467700000t" end="12481000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">结束了吗</p>
<p begin="12484400000t" end="12512300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">不对 这未免太滑稽了</p>
<p begin="12621800000t" end="12634900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">蠢货</p>
<p begin="12660700000t" end="12670200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">莉迪娅？</p>
<p begin="12812000000t" end="12832600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">你这大蠢货</p>
<p begin="12844000000t" end="12854600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">姐姐？</p>
<p begin="12863800000t" end="12897300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">你还是老样子啊 一点没变</p>
<p begin="12903000000t" end="12938800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">姐姐 我 我…</p>
<p begin="12942700000t" end="12976100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">听我说 希尔菲 别责怪巴尔</p>
<p begin="12985200000t" end="12999700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">他没错</p>
<p begin="13030300000t" end="13064100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">而且这世界还没那么差</p>
<p begin="13069300000t" end="13083400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">你要好好活下去</p>
<p begin="13093700000t" end="13109500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">你要是能尽全力活下来</p>
<p begin="13112200000t" end="13148600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">届时我们再相见吧 希尔菲</p>
<p begin="13163800000t" end="13176500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">姐姐</p>
<p begin="13277400000t" end="13294300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">混账东西吗</p>
<p begin="13430100000t" end="13508400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">超乎想像的未来正等待你发现</p>
<p begin="13508400000t" end="13572800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">打开大门的钥匙就在心中</p>
<p begin="13627500000t" end="13696800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">只要伸出你的手</p>
<p begin="13696800000t" end="13743900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">连未来都能改变</p>
<p begin="13743900000t" end="13814500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">冲动 渴望 重新开始</p>
<p begin="13821500000t" end="13868300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">如果要转世 请不要畏惧</p>
<p begin="13868300000t" end="13910000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">向甜美的过去告别</p>
<p begin="13914000000t" end="13960800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">在这日渐昏暗的世界</p>
<p begin="13960800000t" end="13993300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">随波逐流所无法掌握的自由</p>
<p begin="13993300000t" end="14046300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">去追求它吧</p>
<p begin="14051000000t" end="14082500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">舍弃孤独的强大</p>
<p begin="14084600000t" end="14119800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">追求相互理解的温暖</p>
<p begin="14119800000t" end="14154200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">去找出那道光</p>
<p begin="14154200000t" end="14191800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">轻轻抱在怀里前行吧</p>
